    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008860/extras/fb65ab2a467f22eec824aef03b73a20f.poster.avif?t=1727700643\" width=384 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008860/extras/fb65ab2a467f22eec824aef03b73a20f.webm?t=1727700643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008860/extras/fb65ab2a467f22eec824aef03b73a20f.mp4?t=1727700643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BANAN'EM UP</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BANAN'EM UP! is a tiny challenging arcade shoot’em up where you shoot down quirky aliens to save your planet. Evade bullets, shoot enemies, get upgrades, survive for challenging waves to defeat the final boss, &quot;The MONKE&quot;. Die, learn, repeat: get stronger, be powerful!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👾20 handcrafted and hard levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏰20 mins of playtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀6 unique upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹️Perfect 128x128 arcade look and feel powered by Pico8</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008860/extras/284f235c7d2a4c0f9dd616a2444836af.avif?t=1727700643\" width=200 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Hi, it's SkyBrave! I make short games every month! Join my Discord channel to stay connected!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game made thanks to the LazyDevs Academy, I followed his shmup tutorial to add new features and levels to the game. Please support him, he's amazing!</i></p>",
